			<h2>Correspondence</h2>
			<a class="xsmall link-alt" href="https://www.thesunmagazine.org/letter-to-the-editor">Write a Letter to the Editor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>
		</div>

		<div id="article-correspondences" class="correspondences correspondences-collapsed">
								<div class="block-correspondence" id="1422">
		<blockquote class="quote-2">
			<p>I was contemplating suicide when my August 2007 copy of <em>The Sun</em> came, and I read the essay &ldquo;<a href="/article/3699">Confinement</a>&rdquo; by Dorian Gossy. I was so moved by her story of fighting cancer and dealing with the horrors of chemotherapy that I burst into tears. I decided if she could con&shy;tinue on with her life in the state she was in, so could I.</p>
							<p class="quote-2-author">Name Withheld<br></p>
					</blockquote>
	</div>

