				<h3 class="block-content-title"><a href="/issues/513/when-a-guy-helps-you-out">When A Guy Helps You Out</a></h3>
					<p class="block-content-subtitle subtitle"></p>
		

							<ul class="block-content-meta list-inline-border tiny"><li>
